wealthy /ˈwɛlθɪ/

(wealthier,wealthiest) 

1. ADJ Someone who is wealthy has a large amount of money, property, or valuable possessions. 富有的 

例： ...a wealthy international businessman. …一个富有的跨国商人。 

2. N-PLURAL The wealthy are people who are wealthy. 富人 

